        "timestamp": "2019-01-16 05:15:06.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nas an initial commit with dummy placeholders, it looks fine.\nthe schema resources should probably come from the aai-schema JAR rather than making yet another copy of the XSD files.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
