        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-01-16 08:41:41.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n@Keong I agree, since the schema-service is not yet available I used the xsd to get vertex names so that I have some dummy data to play with. When schema-service is ready I will be pulling the data from it of course",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
